            errnum: The number of the error.

        Returns:
            A Pointer to the error message.

        Notes:
            [Reference](https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man3/strerror.3p.html).
            Fn signature: `char *strerror(int errnum)`.
        """

        @parameter
        if static:
